If you were in a Python shell with LaVissa on PYTHONPATH:

from modules.sentience import SentienceEngine, SentienceConfig, RhizomeNode
from lavissa_core import TRPConfig

cfg = SentienceConfig(trp_config=TRPConfig(t_min=0.5, lambda_u=0.5))
engine = SentienceEngine(cfg)

node = RhizomeNode(node_id="alpha", state=[0.1, -0.2, 0.3], echo_id="alpha_echo")
engine.add_node(node)

p_R = [0.5, 0.5]
p_P = [0.4, 0.6]
u = [0.1, -0.1]

result = engine.step_node("alpha", p_R, p_P, u)
print(result)

That would run a full sentience step with TRP + Collapse Law + Eternity echo.
